Long Wind - Not that useful since the introduction of End Regen potions.<br>
Tireless - Seriously needs work to be useful<br>
Regeneration - No idea. I've never looked at it.<br>
Toughness - Some people like this one but there are too many others needed for it to be worth it for me.<br>
Mastery of Water - Totally useless.<br>
Avoidance of Magic - Not worth it since it was nerfed.<br>
Lifter - Maybe<br>
Veil Recovery - Useless.<br>
Mastery of Parry - Nope. Parrying just is too limited in usefulness for a Merc<br>
Mastery of Arms - Since it's been fixed it might be worthwhile if using slower weapons but I tend hit hit speed cap without it. A maybe though.<br>
