Determination - Yes and if it's nerfed I'll likely leave DAoC. Without it tanks are dogmeat in RvR.<br>
Prevent Flight - An absolute necessity.<br>
First Aid/Ignore Pain - A maybe. I don't run with groups that don't have 2 clerics and a pally so it's not that useful but can be worthwhile for when they're mezzed. Still for me it's not worth the points which I prefer putting in to RAs that increase damage.<br>
