Second Wind - Not worth the cost<br>
Rain of XXX - To expensive for what you get.<br>
Empty Mind - Truthfully I've never looked closely at this one.<br>
Purge - An absolute necessity<br>
Void - The concept sounds good but it REALLY needs work to be worth the cost.<br>
<br>
